findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeAccount() and _getReflectionRate() use loops to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list and evaluate total supply respectively, which can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Wrong reflection from token calculations
findings.description: Missing parentheses when calculating target value.

findings.title: No checking if dev address is excluded
findings.description: There is no checking if dev address is excluded from reward in _transfer function, so if it would be, token balance of dev address won’t increase.
